parameters: Clea (If you don't talk to the guild leader)

Former Imperial Dark Division Luid: 'I won't let anyone lay
a finger on Prince Lex. Just as you risked your life for
him, I will also definitely keep my promise.'
Guild Leader Agonia: I will have Clea pave the way.
Clea: Understood. Should we aim for the Photizona Palace?

Guild Leader Agonia: That's right, Atu should be waiting
for us at the front.

Thief Nora: You're really going all out...!? Ugh... just
imagining it makes my body tremble.
Priestess Sophia: I see... Are we going to be the decoys?

Mage Relm: Huh, is that really how it's going to be!? Wait,
I can't agree with that at all!

Guild Leader Agonia: Atu's aim is to flank and annihilate
the Prince's faction, including us, in front of the palace.

Guild Leader Agonia: The other combatants will eliminate
everyone except for Atu's team. I want Clea and the others
to buy us some time.

Guild Leader Agonia: Above all, he desires strong opponents
and will fight without any tricks. I have determined that
Clea and the others are the ones who can stop Atu with our
current forces.

Clea: I think we can endure, but it might be difficult for
us to take them down on our own.

Clea: I have personally experienced the same kind of
pressure as facing a dragon when I crossed swords with such
a formidable monster.

Guild Leader Agonia: It is my job to checkmate everyone
until the check.
Guild Leader Agonia: I will ambush and kill Atu.

Guild Leader Agonia: I want a momentary opening. Please
keep Atu engaged in battle for that purpose.
Clea: ...Is that really okay, Guild Leader?

Guild Leader Agonia: This is the bond of trust between him
and me. We won't betray each other, lie, or run away.

Guild Leader Agonia: I will just fulfill my role. Please
let me know when you are ready.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Guild Leader Agonia: Are you ready to go?
Clea: Please give me a little more time to prepare.

Guild Leader Agonia: Please prepare thoroughly, but
understand that we don't have much time.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Guild Leader Agonia: Please go through the Fotizona Avenue.
There should be some grunts there, but you don't have to
engage with them.
Guild Leader Agonia: I'm counting on you.
Guild Leader Agonia: Please be careful.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
//クエストフラグをリセット
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Storge of Love: It's become quite a situation, hasn't it?
Really.

Storge of Love: Picking a fight with the Empire... Haha, if
I told my past self that, they would probably faint.

Celis, the Gale: This might be a big job since the dragon
subjugation. There's a possibility that we might not be able
to see some people anymore.

Celis, the Gale: That's why we must survive no matter what.
If we're not alive, we won't be able to protect anyone.

Maid Amina: Thank you for persuading Prince Rex. This is
necessary for Lloyd to take a new step forward.

Maid Amina: At the same time, it's also important to me...
I suppose.

One-armed Opro: There were quite a few skilled warriors
gathered here, but what will happen if the monsters are
thrown into battle...

One-armed Opro: Well, how many of them can I hunt down
today?

Explorer Armada: Ahaha, it was tough being cried on by
Ect!

Explorer Armada: We need to quickly settle this and put
Ect, the crybaby, at ease!

Voice Priestess Phoni: I have also spoken with Father. As
the new priestess, I will show that I can save many people.

Voice Priestess Phoni: So... please make sure you don't
die, okay?

Sister Eleo: ...Hah! I'm fine, I'm just a little, well,
quite nervous!

Sister Eleo: But I will also fight. I'm not good at combat,
but leave the healing to me!
Cors the Wanderer: Sigh, this is truly out of place.

Cors the Wanderer: It's quite burdensome when surviving
becomes a condition, not just winning.

Goat of the Bulk Gang: 'Hahaha, I've been eagerly waiting
for this day! I'm grateful for being invited to the greatest
battlefield!'

Goat of the Bulk Gang: The Bulk Gang is the strongest
warriors, and this is a perfect opportunity to show it to
the entire empire!

Prince Rex: I am grateful for Casaro's cooperation in
securing the support of the guild and for stalling them as I
have heard of their achievements from my vassals.

Guild Leader Agonia: The real battle starts now. If we
don't defeat Caron, everything could become our enemy.

Prince Rex: That's right, if we don't win, we'll lose
everything. I must show the power to defeat Caron.

Guild Leader Agonia: It's raining now, which might be
somewhat convenient for us.

Prince Rex: I want you to gather those who will participate
in the operation. There is something I must convey to
everyone.

Prince Rex: First of all, I would like to thank you all for
choosing someone legitimate rather than an evil person.

Prince Rex: According to the information, they are not only
using the dark forces, but also monsters to obstruct our
justice.

Prince Rex: However, with me and all of you, we will
eliminate Caron and his gang from the royal palace, and
Fotizona will be reborn as an empire of order and justice
once again.

Prince Rex: I am the guarantee! As long as I am the king,
the empire's order and justice will never waver!

Prince Rex: I will personally enter the royal palace and
defeat Caron.

Prince Rex: It is said that even during the founding of the
kingdom, there was a thunderstorm like today.

Prince Rex: The previous kings themselves wielded swords
and headed to the battlefield! When the rain clears, the
throne will be vacant for the rightful person!

Prince Rex: Brave warriors! Seasoned heroes! I will lead
the way! Grasp your swords!

Prince Rex: The sword I wield will pave the way! The one
who sits on the throne shall be the legitimate and new king,
Rex!
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Prince Rex: I was able to make it here today thanks to the
Adventurer's Guild.

Prince Rex: I will express my gratitude properly after
becoming king.

Prince Rex: In the empire, the king is not an absolute
existence. There are political battles with the Senate and
powerful nobles.

Prince Rex: In that sense, I think all the previous kings
were lonely on the throne.

Prince Rex: How do you, who have fought in solitude without
anyone believing in the existence of dragons, feel?

Depending on Clea's response, the current quest will change
from Ruling the Empire to Sitting on the Throne.
レクス王子まで孤独な王になる必要はないのでは？
私にはわかりかねます……
レクス王子まで孤独な王になる必要はないのでは？

Clea: I cannot say for certain about the way a king should
be, but Prince Rex is someone who can overturn common sense
and become a king.

Clea: We were able to make the impossible possible because
we had each other as comrades.

Clea: When you feel lonely, please try stepping down from
the throne for a moment. There should be many comrades who
admire you as a prince, not just subjects.

Clea: Sophia-san, of course, there are people here who are
willing to fight alongside me and wield swords.

Clea: Please don't forget that, and become a new king of
the empire who is not alone.
Clea: We fight for the sake of such a new king.

Prince Rex: Your words resonate with me, just like they did
during the battle with Pido... Thank you, not just for
sitting on the throne as the next king.

Prince Rex: To truly aim for the [new king], it is with
many others who share the same aspirations.
私にはわかりかねます……

Clea: I'm sorry, but I can't understand the way a king
should be.

Clea: That is exactly what Prince Rex should be thinking,
and our job is to make Prince Rex into King Rex.

Prince Rex: You're right. What lies ahead as a king is my
responsibility, and it is my battle.

Prince Rex: Asking such a boring question in the first
place, isn't that just being spoiled?

Prince Rex: ...I will prepare myself for the loneliness of
the throne from now on.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Prince Rex: Finally, we will infiltrate the royal palace.

Prince Rex: I have high expectations for your work. Please
help me pave the way to the throne.

Fushichiya's Shimosu: 'We are adventurers who fight for
ourselves. Risk your lives for the future of the guild and
Futeira.'

Receptionist Piste: Things are progressing rapidly, and
before we know it, we'll end up infiltrating the royal
palace...

Receptionist Piste: I can only offer my support, but I'll
be praying for everyone's safe return!

Young explorer Ect: I have a feeling that there's something
I can grasp after going through this battle.

Young explorer Ect: And I absolutely want to protect the
place that Papa loved and the friends that Papa loved!

Captain Clevo: I don't think this will be enough to atone,
but I believe this battle has meaning for me as well.

Captain Clevo: Even someone like me might be able to
protect something. If this battle ends safely, I feel like
I'll be able to believe that.
